    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for anyone prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with noticeable paint fading on the roof and hood, along with several minor scratches and dings consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean but displays typical wear, including some fraying on the driver's seat bolster and minor staining in the rear carpet. Mechanically, the car has been well-maintained and runs smoothly, though it lacks the polish of a newer model. It is a solid, honest car that delivers reliable transportation at an affordable price point.",
