      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior, has been maintained to an exacting standard. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this motorcar offers an uncompromising driving experience for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection.",
