    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It is honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it really shows in how it looks and drives. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect ride that feels brand new, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look, I promise you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
