    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s M-division engineering, featuring the S54 3.2L inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS system. The valvetrain has been precision-shimmed, and the rod bearings have been proactively addressed to ensure mechanical longevity. Power is routed through a crisp ZF 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional lateral grip and exit-traction. The chassis maintains its factory-intended torsional rigidity, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and original-spec bushings. Meticulously preserved with documented service intervals, this vehicle retains its sharp turn-in and neutral handling balance, offering a pure, naturally aspirated driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 33
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No cosmetic or mechanical flaws. Full service records available. Clean title.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
