    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its initial purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with zero imperfections, complemented by flawless alloy wheels and premium tires. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the leather seating is supple and devoid of any wear, and every electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a complete service history from the authorized dealership and recent preventative maintenance performed. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this car offers an unrivaled driving experience. It comes with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
