      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total dream. This car has been meticulously babied since day one\u2014always garaged, hand-washed, and kept in truly flawless condition. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership price tag, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
